Name: GinRat2024
Authors: G Becq et al. see ref 0
Description: The reference anatomical template is a copy of the Tohoku template from the work of Valdés-Hernández et al. (see ref 1), adapted to the resolution of our study and given in a RAS coordinates system (see ref 0). The orientation is RAS. The origin is at Bregma (0, 0, 0).
